bdcomPibToMib.name: bdcomPibToMib
bdcomPibToMib.description: bdcomPibToMib is the root of the BDCOM-assigned OID subtree for MIBs which are algorithmically generated/translated from BDCOM PIBs with OIDs assigned under the bdcomPIB subtree. These generated MIBs allow management entities (other the current Policy Server) to read the downloaded policy. By convention, for PIB 'bdcomPIB.x', the generated MIB shall have the name 'bdcomPibToMib.x'.
